Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.62,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\b0\bord3.5\blur10.5\pos(318,610)\3c&H0E1533&}我是毕斯可!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.94,Title,,0,0,0,,弓矢的两人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的已经是最高时速了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要怪就怪你的摩托坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,接你的时候顺便在宫城基地发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个铁人的说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你专心开车就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,松手  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,放手  很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种外行看不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是血气方刚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的和美禄有血缘关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没有相信你是我弟弟的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样的云游商人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,做了这么多怎么可能不求回报
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点上你是说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只有傻子才会为别人去拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到霜吹驻军地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的部下在那里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,美禄  我马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前一定要平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们都活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,伤得好重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看来机械玩偶一爆炸  世界就毁灭了的传说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是童话故事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我从那个铁人中感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,许多古人苦苦追求的  一种近乎执念的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,执念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那压倒性的力量了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不单单是金属
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它能锈蚀所有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,植物  动物还有人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,锈蚀到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛既是支配万物的恐怖之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,也是无法对抗的强大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要说的话就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然而食锈却可以吞噬锈蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,它能利用锈蚀支配生命的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果锈蚀是死神的话  那食锈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,简单来说  就是死神克星了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,锈蚀和蕈菇的力量之间  是否存在某种关联呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过肯定的是  蕈菇是跟着锈蚀进化的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs46\bord3\be20\pos(650,715)}他们在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs46\bord3\be20\pos(650,715)}没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口很深  暂时你要静养
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道那东西会往哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我刚才看到了他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那是孤独的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定会回忌滨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这次别死了  毕斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可还没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他的灵魂存续下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这小子的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正兰亭圆_GBK\fs46\bord3\be20\pos(640,715)}发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  来算总账吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙  纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有东西过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,商人的话就赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有个大的不得了的巨人往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快看  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹  那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见过也没听说过那种怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是铁人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,骨骼的形状和这个镇子一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那是活着的铁人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,距离多远?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大概三千米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,前进方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,径直朝我们这边走过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不做些什么的话  镇子会被毁掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,难道要和它战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么可能打得过那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个镇子可是祖辈们守下来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们离开镇子吧  纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,幸助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都理解你不希望这个镇子被毁的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔贝罗的灵魂在我们身上  而不在镇子上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,镇子无论被摧毁多少次  也能够重建起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有你和我们在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,自从见过赤星后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你小子说话硬气多了啊  幸助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大家听好  准备开撤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人都不准死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停  都跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的镇子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我留下来拖住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算去死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能去  纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我去展现一下卡尔贝罗渔夫的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看这边  大块头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔贝罗最好的鱼叉手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,白鲸钓手纳兹来会会你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,冲我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看我一叉子叫你上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,听我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才打不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以跑来欺负小孩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,白熊猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…美禄吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无论金钱还是权力  乃至强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最终都没能拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但你放心  黑革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我来跟你彻底做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  让我们继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,白…白熊猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹  干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我看到了卡尔贝罗渔夫的真正胆力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你去保护大家  趁现在赶紧逃远一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,纳兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们趁这个时候逃去高台那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,黑革
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么只有熊猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,赤星怎么没来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,帕乌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,滋露…你们怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我跑去大路上时  碰巧遇上了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,托她们的福  我好好休息了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你真的还活着呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,厉害啊  熊猫小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等会儿再叙旧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,忌滨自警团来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩交给他们保护吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它开溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,来结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,外面是不是有些吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,听说自警团倾巢出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,反正又是在搞演习之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们几个  别摸鱼好好干活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,出大事了  快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点  美禄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  有东西要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我有不好的预感  离它远点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙不妙不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,帕乌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,贾维爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋  只能这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,差一点都能赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,红色的药剂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是毘沙门菇毒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身体是吃不消的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是毕斯可…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你还会阻止我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,替我照顾好帕乌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,打
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了这一炮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你该长点记性了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,黑革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,熊猫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,美禄  不要冲动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我还站着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可之前也是这种心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我可以射箭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,像毕斯可一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,美禄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,毕斯可?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在黄泉的跟前  我听到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,射箭有两个要领
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一个是要仔细观察
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个是相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  弓矢的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你会射中的  毕斯可
Comment: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:08.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,
